rComments: I've taken a few classes with Stec, he is always super interesting and really evokes great conversation. It's a pleasure to be in his classes.

Attended this class with above-average video editing and computer technology experience. This class should not be a problem for you if you have these experiences. In addition, he tries his best to understand and make happy the students. He is a very good and caring teacher.
Great teacher. Thoughtful and clearly cares about his students. Lots of projects but they are interesting and engaging!
